data.description: Sellers are offering $8,000 towards closing costs. Welcome to this beautiful home in The Ponds. When you walk in the front door you are greeted by 10' ceilings with 8' doors that leads to an open concept living. Your spacious family room next to the kitchen with a large island and a huge walk-in pantry. The mother-in-law suite is in the back on the first floor. There is a nice loft space at the top of the stairs that leads to the bedrooms.  The master has a tray ceiling and walk in closet.  There are 2 more bedrooms on the second floor. Leaving through the back door is a screened in porch that leads to the garage and a side yard.  There is a nice green space around the corner from the back yard. The Ponds community has walking trails, dog park, pool, fishing ponds, YMCA and a fire stationYour spacious family room next to the kitchen with a large island and a huge walk-in pantry.
